s a `promises` property for the Promise-based API:\n\n```ts\nconst data = await vol.promises.readFile('/hello.txt', 'utf8');\n```\n\n## License\n\nApache-2.0\n","repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/streamich/memfs.git"},"_source_registry_name":"default","bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/streamich/memfs/issues"}}